data.description: Seller offering buy-down concessions to make this home more affordable in this market! Welcome to the epitome of charm and comfort in the heart of Elizabethtown, Kentucky! Presenting an immaculately cared-for 1.5-story Cape Cod that defines the perfect blend of modern amenities and classic appeal. As you pull up, notice the stunning curb appeal, complemented by a pristine new roof and meticulously manicured landscaping. The pride of ownership continues as you step inside, greeted by a seamless flow of new carpet and flooring throughout, creating an inviting atmosphere in every corner. Experience the luxury of a home that has been thoughtfully upgraded with a new HVAC system, ensuring optimal comfort and energy efficiency. The entire home features new windows, allowing an abundance of natural light to fill each room, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The home boasts a new hot water heater just inspected by the city and brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the living room, dinning room, and kitchen. One of the standout features of this property is the recently added two-car garage, a true haven for car enthusiasts and hobbyists alike. This garage is not just any garage – it comes complete with a built-in air compressor, its own electric meter, and the added bonus of heating and air conditioning.  Located in the heart of Elizabethtown, convenience is at your fingertips, with easy access to local amenities, schools, and entertainment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this beautiful property home – with its combination of timeless charm and modern upgrades, it won't last long on the market. Schedule your showing today and envision the life of comfort and style that awaits you in this picture-perfect Cape Cod residence!
